   "mcqTrap": "- Distractor: **'A low LRINEC score (<6) safely excludes necrotising fasciitis, so manage as cellulitis with oral antibiotics'** — WRONG and dangerous\n  - NF is a **clinical/surgical diagnosis**; LRINEC cannot exclude it",
